#after-bid-modal.medium.reveal-modal data-reveal=""
  .row
    .small-12.columns
      h2
        | Thank you for bidding
    .small-12.columns
      h5
        | You will receive a bid confirmation in your email shortly.

  .row
    .small-12.columns
      hr
      h3
        | What now?
    .small-12.large-6.columns
      h5
        | 1. Get your friends to join you!
      div
        a href="mailto:" style="margin-right: 5px;"
          i.fa.fa-envelope.fa-3x
        a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=#{request.original_url}" target="_blank" style="margin-right: 5px;"
          i.fa.fa-facebook-square.fa-3x
        - message = "Just bid on: '#{@auction.title}'! #{@short_url}"
        a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?hashtags=timeauction%2Cmoneycantbuy&text=#{message}" target="_blank"
          i.fa.fa-twitter-square.fa-3x

    .small-12.large-6.columns
      h5
        | 2. Do more volunteering :)
      div
        - if @auction.program && !@auction.program.volunteer_opportunities_link.blank?
          = link_to "Find volunteering opportunities", @auction.program.volunteer_opportunities_link, :class => "button primary"
        - else
          = link_to "Find volunteering opportunities", opportunities_path, :class => "button primary"

